sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Service as modelmesh-serving Service<br/>8033 gRPC / 8008 HTTP
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>UDS/8001 gRPC
    participant ETCD as ETCD<br/>2379/TCP gRPC/HTTP<br/>Optional TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS Signature V4

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>Service: POST /infer<br/>gRPC (8033/TCP)<br/>No encryption<br/>Optional app-level auth
    Service->>ModelMesh: Forward request<br/>gRPC
    ModelMesh->>ETCD: Lookup model metadata<br/>gRPC/HTTP<br/>Optional TLS
    ETCD-->>ModelMesh: Model location & config
    ModelMesh->>Runtime: Inference request<br/>gRPC via UDS or 8001/TCP
    Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
    ModelMesh-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>Client: JSON/Protobuf response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: REST Inference Request

    Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTP (8008/TCP)<br/>No encryption<br/>Optional app-level auth
    Service->>RESTProxy: Forward HTTP request<br/>8008/TCP
    RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP
    ModelMesh->>Runtime: Inference request<br/>gRPC
    Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
    ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>Service: HTTP response
    Service-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: InferenceService Creation

    Client->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate request<br/>HTTPS 9443/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>K8s API cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
    K8sAPI-->>Client: Resource created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Model Loading from Storage

    participant Puller as Storage Puller<br/>Init Container<br/>8086 gRPC
    participant SharedVol as Shared Volume

    Puller->>K8sAPI: Read storage-config Secret<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Puller: S3 credentials
    Puller->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS Signature V4
    S3-->>Puller: Model files
    Puller->>SharedVol: Write to shared volume<br/>Filesystem
    Runtime->>SharedVol: Read model files<br/>Filesystem
    Runtime->>ModelMesh: Model ready notification<br/>gRPC

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 5: Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant ControllerMetrics as Controller Metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RuntimeMetrics as Runtime Metrics<br/>2112/TCP HTTP

    Prometheus->>ControllerMetrics: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    ControllerMetrics-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
    Prometheus->>RuntimeMetrics: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP 2112/TCP<br/>No encryption
    RuntimeMetrics-->>Prometheus: Runtime pod metrics
